Comment: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul?
Comment: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}It's like a fear　悪い夢の様で
Comment: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}目覚めても　All I've got is bones
Comment: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}I'm in a panic? Get out, hurry
Comment: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Oh, there're mysteries and miseries
Comment: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Dead or alive　狭間に揺られて
Comment: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}彷徨えば　Right to left to hell
Comment: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}孤独の招待　感情の消退
Comment: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
Comment: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:26.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}仮面の淵へ　手を掛けどただ骨が鳴るのみ
Comment: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Wars and swords, tears and blood
Comment: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:33.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}溢る力が　不意に嗤い出した
Comment: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:39.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Comment: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Comment: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:49.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
Comment: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}理解らない　構わない
Comment: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}紛い力振るっても
Comment: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:59.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただこの世界を生き抜けよ
Comment: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:04.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}嗚呼　失くした哀しみがまた疼いてく…
Comment: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Misery-World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真實在何處  我四處探尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:51.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我魂在何方
